properties.Name: PolicyholderCurrencyUsage
properties.Description:
The various uses or applications of the associated Language regarding the Policyholder for the associated period.

Ex:

- Bill Payment = US$
- Claim Proceeds = Sfr
- Dividend Payment = US$
- Investment Currency = Euro

Columns.Name: CurrencyUsageId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Currency Use.

Columns.Name: PeriodStartDate
Columns.Description: The period start date for which the Currency Use(s) are defined.

Columns.Name: PeriodEndDate
Columns.Description: The period end date for which the Currency Use(s) are defined.

Columns.Name: Note
Columns.Description: Notes, comments or additional information regarding the application of the associated Currency for the Policyholder.

Columns.Name: PolicyholderId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Policyholder.
